titleStmt.title: A Declaration of the agreement of the 11. of Janvary, betwixt His Majesty and the inhabitants of the county of Oxon for provisions for His Majesties horses billited in this county.
titleStmt.author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1625-1649 : Charles I)

notesStmt.note: A London counterfeit of "An explanation of the agreement of the 21 of Decemb." with title and date of agreement falsified. cf. Madan.
